title._content: Faculty Ladies Riding Class who will give spectacular exhibition at the Pendleton Rodeo Contest

description._content: Image Description: During Military Tournaments in Pendleton Rodeo contest. At the far left is Mrs. Batcheller. The fourth person from the left is Helen Moore. Lula May Brandtl is the seventh person from the left.
